<div class="page-section__sub-section">
	<h4>Align Self</h4>
	<p>The align-self property is applied directly to the flex items. The alignment options follow the same rules for the align-items property, the only difference is it's directly applied to a flex item instead of a flex box. You can choose from <code>.align-self-start</code>, <code>.align-self-end</code>, <code>.align-self-center</code>, <code>.align-self-baseline</code> and <code>.align-self-stretch</code>.</p>
